    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Artificial surfaces designed to facilitate practicing rock climbing techniques, providing the climber with varying surface textures, grips, scale, and inclination.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
